Step 3 (2 pts)

ggplot(penguins, aes(y=bill_depth_mm, x=bill_length_mm, color = species)) + geom_point() +
  labs(
    title = "Bill Length vs Bill Depth of Penguins",
    x = "Bill Length (mm)",
    y = "Bill Depth (mm)"
